58f8c2415a9349edd","tid":235180,"uid":115481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全明白 我屋企都應該會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢現時根本無得揀 <br />\n唯有同自己講爲左個仔忍耐下啦<br />\n到佢小學可以鬆d就偷偷見工<br />\n之後就搬 再離婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢同我講佢有抑鬱 好驚有一日會忍唔住壓力自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢捱唔捱到多幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c8a5812b2f57ead45364831b32c881f40bbafa","tid":235180,"uid":45268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"個女仔咁都忍到4,5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe663d782d413c200ee9337f22738927090fd7f","tid":235180,"uid":115481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個女仔咁都忍到4,5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個女到宜家反而可能係佢精神支柱"},{"pid":"c38249c98312caec87def1283961f02ae620ca81","tid":235180,"uid":36033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全明白 我屋企都應該會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢現時根本無得揀 <br />\n唯有同自己講爲左個仔忍耐下啦<br />\n到佢小學可以鬆d就偷偷見工<br />\n之後就搬 再離婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢同我講佢有抑鬱 好驚有一日會忍唔住壓力自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢捱唔捱到多幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來有個女 睇錯咗 叫佢去搵吓d姑娘傾下<br />\n你又多d同佢傾下計 唔好同佢傾唔開心既事<br />\n等佢可以有段時間鬆下 唔好諗唔開心嘅事<br />\n最快就捱完咖啦 <br />\n最緊要到時佢勇敢d離開佢老公"}]}